tourBios.curYrHigh: Joined PGA TOUR Latinoamérica by finishing T9 at the Sebring, FL Q-School in January. Secured full status for the first half of the season as one of the players who survived a five-man playoff for three spots inside top-11.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Played Division II golf at Eckerd College, where he earned all-conference selections as a junior and senior.
tourBios.personal: Has one brother, Brandon... Attended Abington Heights HS in Clarks Summit, PA... Rafa Nadal and Tom Brady are his favorite athletes outside of golf... The Boston Red Sox and the New England Patriots are his favorite pro teams... Stowe Mountain GC in Stowe, VT is the golf course he has liked the most... His personal motto is "Work before glory."... Would like to trade places for a day with Jordan Spieth... On his time off he drives for Uber.
tourBios.exmtStatus: Exempt - Finished 2-11 at 2016 Q-School (exempt to midseason reshuffle)

dyn.dynStats: He ranks T45th in Par Breakers on the Latinoamérica.
